data.text:
The Tower Of Power is The Gym Chef’s one stop item for all your seasoning needs, the pack includes our signature range of the original 6 flavours all compiled into one neatly packed, easy to store, Tower!

The Tower includes the following 50g tubs:

PERI PERI - Our own take on a spicy Portuguese Peri Peri flavour, the best addition to your grilled meats.

TANDOORI - A popular Indian seasoning that packs a big hit of flavour without all the hidden additives and nasties!

GARLIC AND HERB - If you’re a mellow fellow look no further, aromatic Garlic and a nice range of herbs, add to your pastas and even your cheese on toast!

LEMON AND HERB- If you’re a lover of a nice flakey baked fish then this is the seasoning blend for you, amazing companion for your Salmon and even Chicken thighs!

SMOKE AND SPICE- BBQ fans unite, lets get our smoke and spice on tonight, our own take on a Smokey chipotle BBQ flavour with an added kick of heat. Amazing on your morning eggs and can even transform a simple chicken breast!

ALL PURPOSE - Not too spicy, not too mild, just right! A big customer favourite as it can be added to pretty much anything for that extra punch of flavour.

Our seasoning blends are:

All natural with no nasties

Contain no added salt or sugar

Free from artificial colourings

No additives or preservatives

Unique concentrated flavour - No other seasoning like this on the market

High pepper content to encourage a thermogenic reaction to help boost metabolism.

Each 50g tub is enough to inject flavour into 10-20 meals!

Guideline Nutritional Information

A typical pot contains:

Per 100g Per 5g serving Energy kJ 1719 85.95 kcal 408 20.4 FAT 11.1 0.555 of which Saturates 1.6 0.08 Carbohydrates 60.3 3.015 of which Sugars 19.8 0.99 Protein 16.7 0.835 Salt 0.13 0.0065

Ingredients (per pot):

PERI PERI: Paprika, Chilli Flakes, Garlic Powder, Chilli Powder, Lemon Powder Mixed Herbs, Onion Powder; Dried Coriander, Black Pepper, Cayenne Pepper.

TANDOORI: Garlic, Dried Coriander, Crushed Chillies, Red Chilli, Paprika, Ginger, Cumin, Coriander, Turmeric, Dried Fenugreek, Black Pepper, Mango, Lemon Peel Powder.

GARLIC AND HERB: Garlic Flakes, Garlic Powder, Onion Powder, Mustard Powder, Dried Parsley, Pepper, Mixed Herbs.

LEMON AND HERB: Lemon Peel Powder, Onion Powder, Dried Rosemary, Ground pepper, Italian Herbs, Dried Parsley.

SMOKE AND SPICE: Smoke Paprika, Garlic, Chilli, Cumin, Onion Powder, Mustard, Coriander, Black Pepper, Crushed Chillies.

ALL PURPOSE: Paprika, Garlic, Italian Herbs, Ground Mustard, Parsley, Onion Powder, Black Pepper, Cayenne Pepper.
